 Infrastructure Build v1.0.5
 ===========================
 Base OS : CentOS7

 This node runs :
 - Docker
 - Filebeat to send logs to TRADR Services VBOX ELK instance
 - Syslog NG
 - NTPD
 - MariaDB Server
 - Wazuh HIDS
 - Logrotate
 - TRADR Application (Dockerised)

 For X windows forwarding from another workstation use :
 $ vagrant ssh -- -Y
 $ xterm

 You are currently logged into the TRADR VirtualBox.

 Instructions
 ============
 [1] Iceberg Commands :
 Type 'help_tradr'        : Display instructions
 Type 'upgrade'           : Upgrade the TRADR (Dockerised) applications
 Type 'backup'            : Backup your TRADR SQL configuration and data
 Type 'backup-lts'        : Backup your LTS TRADR SQL configuration and data
 Type 'restore'           : Restore your TRADR SQL configuration and data
 Type 'restore-LTS'       : Restore your LTS TRADR SQL configuration and data

 Type 'cli' to access the TRADR command-line interface (admin_cli and user_cli modes)
 [2] admin_cli and user_cli commands:
 ./install_tradr.sh       : Install the complete TRADR Application

